  "detailed_description": "Adventure Allies\" is a casual action-adventure game where you can adventure with monsters and enjoy combat, exploration, and training.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Set out on an adventure to an unknown island</h2>Players set out on an adventure from their base to an unknown island. Explore freely in search of monsters, items, and treasure!<br>After 10 minutes of adventure, the dreaded night will arrive. Get off the island as soon as possible.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003680/extras/142a4597194aff5688c14772e73a1346.poster.avif?t=1735894783\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003680/extras/142a4597194aff5688c14772e73a1346.webm?t=1735894783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003680/extras/142a4597194aff5688c14772e73a1346.mp4?t=1735894783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Join the monsters</h2>Monsters appear here and there on the island. Each monster has unique stats and unique skills.<br>When a monster is given a certain amount of Tame Energy, it becomes a temporary companion.<br>If you succeed in bringing the monster back from the escape point, it becomes a full member of the group.<br>Let's collect various monsters!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003680/extras/84a2d657b0ac3e362e0c8ef2b6e1a5a3.poster.avif?t=1735894783\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003680/extras/84a2d657b0ac3e362e0c8ef2b6e1a5a3.webm?t=1735894783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003680/extras/84a2d657b0ac3e362e0c8ef2b6e1a5a3.mp4?t=1735894783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Synthesis</h2>Monsters can be synthesized to inherit each other's status.<br>Breed the strongest monster you can find!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003680/extras/9d6e7ff350197a2a911f31c9a453e19f.poster.avif?t=1735894783\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003680/extras/9d6e7ff350197a2a911f31c9a453e19f.webm?t=1735894783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003680/extras/9d6e7ff350197a2a911f31c9a453e19f.mp4?t=1735894783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Materials and Shop</h2>You can obtain various materials from monsters and ores during your adventures.<br>Exchange them for items at the stores located at your base and use them to help you conquer your adventures.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003680/extras/0192d02229bba8f37a04d29d8b7c6855.poster.avif?t=1735894783\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003680/extras/0192d02229bba8f37a04d29d8b7c6855.webm?t=1735894783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003680/extras/0192d02229bba8f37a04d29d8b7c6855.mp4?t=1735894783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Equipment</h2>Equipment can be purchased in stores or obtained from monster drops.<br>Players and monsters have equipment slots like a puzzle.<br>Equipment comes in different shapes, so think about what and where you want to place it.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003680/extras/855147c51ce9099fda398e261aef1809.poster.avif?t=1735894783\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003680/extras/855147c51ce9099fda398e261aef1809.webm?t=1735894783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003680/extras/855147c51ce9099fda398e261aef1809.mp4?t=1735894783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The arena</h2>Take on the arena where powerful NPCs await you along with monsters.<br>Winning the arena will give you special items and monsters.<br>Aim to conquer the arena!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003680/extras/753ccd6653aa9e994a397810456de510.poster.avif?t=1735894783\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003680/extras/753ccd6653aa9e994a397810456de510.webm?t=1735894783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003680/extras/753ccd6653aa9e994a397810456de510.mp4?t=1735894783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Big coins and treasures</h2>Large coins and treasures may be found in the field.<br>Large coins have special effects depending on the number of coins collected.<br>Treasures have the effect of increasing the player's status.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003680/extras/25c2c3d22e49d93039fe2422a23185fe.poster.avif?t=1735894783\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003680/extras/25c2c3d22e49d93039fe2422a23185fe.webm?t=1735894783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003680/extras/25c2c3d22e49d93039fe2422a23185fe.mp4?t=1735894783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Communication</h2>Invite your Steam friends to adventure with you.<br>Up to two people can play together.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003680/extras/9b27ef72bd2fe30df4b6ce4f25625136.poster.avif?t=1735894783\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003680/extras/9b27ef72bd2fe30df4b6ce4f25625136.webm?t=1735894783\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003680/extras/9b27ef72bd2fe30df4b6ce4f25625136.mp4?t=1735894783\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Videos and Streaming</h2>The game can be freely distributed on video distribution sites such as YouTube and Twitch.<br>There are no restrictions on monetization. No prior or post contact is required.<br>There are no restrictions on posting on social networking sites.<br>We would appreciate it if you could include the name of the game or the URL of the Steam page in your video or distribution.",
